{"tid":1013303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國學生偷攝美軍事設施　重判入獄一年","createTime":"2019-02-08T08:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T08:59:25.000Z","uid":103759,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"06b4c4b10e9de8abbd74c69ec6bda3a1e4792a2d","tid":1013303,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:47:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/us-05_O6QMm_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fus-05_O6QMm_1200x0.png&h=5e87b1fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名20歲的中國學生，被控違法拍攝佛羅里達西礁島的美軍設施，當地星期二（2月5日）被判監一年。<br />\n<br />\n該名中國學生趙乾利（Zhao Qianli），去年9月26日擅闖在西礁島的「南方聯合跨部門特遣部隊」指揮中心，據調查他曾圍繞指揮中心的圍欄視察，之後在無圍欄的海灘走進中心範圍，用相機和手機影相拍片，附近有警告牌標明是禁區。<br />\n<br />\n趙乾利認罪，但他的代表律師強調，趙乾利是中國中北大學的交流生，事發時是觀光迷路才會誤闖軍事設施，不是間諜；但控方反駁指，他的相機和電話都沒有在景點拍攝的照片，主要都是軍事設施的相片，包括建築物及衛星天線等。法官摩爾 (K. Michael Moore) 對他處以最重的一年徒刑，超過量刑建議的零到六個月，檢方要求判刑九個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/中國學生偷攝美軍事設施-重判入獄一年/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%81%B7%E6%94%9D%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%8B%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%BD-%E9%87%8D%E5%88%A4%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%84%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%2F&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1BURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=e7a86e78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%81%B7%E6%94%9D%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%8B%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%BD-%E9%87%8D%E5%88%A4%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%84%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%2F&h=241264fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/中國學生偷攝美軍事設施-重判入獄一年/</a>"},{"pid":"24e609fe222100523cfdaacab8eaaa6c3ba5df4c","tid":1013303,"uid":161990,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:51:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死支那仔"},{"pid":"c208880c07e7e2be5a468a76eb79a94c3b4